How Easy Tips Calculator work

All you need to do is give the following 3 information:

  • Bill Total: the total amount $ shows on your bill

  • Tips %: percentage of bill total you want to tip them

  • Split Bill: split the bill between any number of people

The following R code shows how to calculate your tips for your $100 bill with 20 % tips and split by 4 persons.

Bill.Total   <- 100      # $ shows on your bill
Tips.Percent <- 0.20     # 20 % tips
Split.Bill   <- 4        # split bill by 4 persons

Tips.Total  <- Bill.Total*Tips.Percent
Final.Total <- Bill.Total + Tips.Total
Split.Total <- round(Final.Total/Split.Bill, 2)

OutPut <- data.frame(Title=c("Bill Total$", 
                             "Tips Total: $",
                             "Final Total: $", 
                             "Tips %:", 
                             "Split Bill by:", 
                             "Split Total Per Person: $"), 
                    Values=c(Bill.Total, Tips.Total, Final.Total, 
                             Tips.Percent, Split.Bill, Split.Total))

Easy Tips Calculator
